headline: IFF Announces Board of Directors Changes
summary: NEW YORK, December 19, 2024--IFF (NYSE: IFF) today unveiled the next phase in the evolution of its Board of Directors, aimed at bolstering the company's long-term strategic vision and driving profitable market share growth.
